    "This section systematically dissects these obstacles and, building on this analysis, charts key research opportunities to guide the continued maturation of the field.",
    "ChallengesThe current challenges fall into three dimensions of quality defects in generated artifacts, architectural limitations of the models themselves, and systemic deficiencies in the evaluation and deployment ecosystem.6.1.1 Quality and Effectiveness of Generated Tests.",
    "A primary challenge concerns the quality and utility of the generated tests.",
    "For any automated test generation technique to be considered viable, its outputs must satisfy a set of quality attributes.",
    "At the most fundamental level, a test must be operationally valid, meaning it is syntactically correct and executable."
